of <br> <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-cyan-300">Residential, Commercial &#038; Industrial Cooling</span></h1><p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 text-slate-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed"> From <strong>Window AC Service Vadodara</strong> to Heavy Chiller Plants. <br>We fix what others can&#8217;t. 24/7 Emergency Support.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4"> <a href="https://wa.me/919727257141" aria-label="Message Atlas Aircon on WhatsApp" class="bg-[#25D366] hover:bg-[#1da851] text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-black text-lg flex items-center justify-center transition shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(37,211,102,0.4)]" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-2xl mr-2"></i> WhatsApp Tech Support </a> <a href="#locations" aria-label="Find Service Areas" class="bg-slate-800/50 hover:bg-slate-700/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center transition">Find Your Area</a></div></div></section><section id="about" class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Vadodara&#8217;s Most Trusted <span class="text-blue-700">Cooling Experts</span></h2><p class="text-slate-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Atlas Aircon isn&#8217;t just a repair shop; we are an engineering firm dedicated to climate control. Whether it&#8217;s a <strong>Window AC repair in Alkapuri</strong> or a <strong>Chiller Plant maintenance in <a href="https://www.atlasaircons.com/?zone=Makarpura+GIDC" style="color:#0ea5e9; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px dashed #0ea5e9;" title="Expert Makarpura GIDC Solutions">Makarpura GIDC</a></strong>, we bring military-grade precision to every job.</p><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center"><div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm"><div class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-700">5k+</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-700 uppercase font-bold mt-1">Repairs</div></div><div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm"><div class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-700">90</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-700 uppercase font-bold mt-1">Min Response</div></div><div class="p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm"><div class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-700">4.9</div><div class="text-xs text-slate-700 uppercase font-bold mt-1">Rating</div></div></div></div><div class="relative"> <img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high"  src="https://www.atlasaircons.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Window-AC-Installation-and-Repairing.webp" alt="AC Service Installation Vadodara" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl z-10 relative" title="Atlas Aircon Home 4"><div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-blue-800 text-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-xl z-20 hidden md:block"><p class="font-bold text-lg">Certified Experts</p><p class="text-sm opacity-90">ISO 9001:2015 Compliant</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id="services" class="section-padding bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-slate-900">Core Services</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="bg-white group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition duration-500"></div><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 text-2xl mb-6"><i class="fa-solid fa-wind"></i></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Window AC Service</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Deep jet cleaning, filter wash, and anti-rust coating for longevity.</p> <a href="/window-ac-service-vadodara" aria-label="Learn more about Window AC Service" class="text-blue-700 font-bold text-sm hover:underline">Learn More</a></div><div class="bg-white group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition duration-500"></div><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 text-2xl mb-6"><i class="fa-solid fa-tools"></i></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Split AC Repair</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Fixing water leakage, gas charging, and PCB repairs on site.</p> <a href="/split-ac-service-vadodara" aria-label="Learn more about Split AC Repair" class="text-blue-700 font-bold text-sm hover:underline">Learn More</a></div><div class="bg-white group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-300 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition duration-500"></div><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 text-2xl mb-6"><i class="fa-solid fa-industry"></i></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Chiller Plants</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">Industrial cooling solutions for GIDC factories and large offices.</p> <a href="/chiller-repair-services-vadodara" aria-label="Learn more about Chiller Plant Maintenance" class="text-blue-700 font-bold text-sm hover:underline">Learn More</a></div></div><div class="mt-12 text-left"><div class="w-full"><div class="mt-8"><h3 