g</span></h2><p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Don&#8217;t guess what&#8217;s wrong. Use our Neuromorphic Diagnostic Terminal to identify the exact fault before deploying an engineer.</p></div><div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto"><div class="atlas-diag-box"><div class="atlas-diag-header"><h3><i class="fas fa-microchip text-sky-500"></i> AI System Diagnostic</h3><p>Select the symptom your HVAC system is experiencing.</p></div><div class="atlas-diag-grid" id="diag-options"> <button class="atlas-diag-btn" onclick="runAtlasDiagnostic('Blowing Warm Air')"><i class="fas fa-temperature-high text-red-500"></i> Blowing Warm Air</button> <button class="atlas-diag-btn" onclick="runAtlasDiagnostic('Water Leaking')"><i class="fas fa-tint text-blue-400"></i> Water Leaking</button> <button class="atlas-diag-btn" onclick="runAtlasDiagnostic('Strange Noise/Vibration')"><i class="fas fa-volume-up text-amber-500"></i> Strange Noises</button> <button class="atlas-diag-btn" onclick="runAtlasDiagnostic('Power Tripping/Dead')"><i class="fas fa-bolt text-yellow-400"></i> Power Tripping</button></div><div class="atlas-diag-loader" id="diag-loader"><div class="atlas-spinner"></div><div style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;">Analyzing Matrix...</div></div><div class="atlas-diag-result" id="diag-result"><h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Critical Fault Detected</h4><p id="diag-msg"></p> <a href="#" id="diag-wa-link" target="_blank" class="atlas-diag-cta"> <i class="fab fa-whatsapp" style="font-size:20px; margin-right:8px;"></i> Request Dispatch to Your Area </a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-12 bg-blue-800 text-white text-center border-t border-blue-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-white"><i class="fas fa-lock text-blue-300"></i> Internal Engineering Dispatch &#038; Log</h2><p class="text-blue-100 text-sm mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-semibold">